      • Shape

        public Shape(Set<Primitive> primitives)
        Creates a shape from a List of primitive objects. All coordinates are in body frame. The origin of this shape must be the center of mass of the shape.
        Parameters:
        primitives - A set of primitives that make up this shape

      • newCylinder

        public static Shape newCylinder(double radius,
                                double length,
                                int rank)
        Creates a vertically oriented cylinder
        Parameters:
        radius - the radius of the cylinder
        length - the length of the cylinder
        rank - the complexity of the shape. Higher numbers lead to more realistic collisions but worse performance. Recommended 10-100.
        Returns:
        The Shape object representing the cylinder.
